data.name: ActivationDatePicker.ToolTip
data.value: Use this to set when the ad should be activated. The time stated is using the Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

data.name: ExpiryDatePicker.ToolTip
data.value: Enable the checkbox to be able to set an expiry date for the ad. Uncheck the checkbox to make the ad never expire. The time stated is in Coordinated Universal Time.

data.name: ImageSizeCombo.ToolTip
data.value:
The image you store must be one of the preset sizes. Note that your cache file should have one of each size stored in it, otherwise you may encounter problems running the game.
Some files may only use the same aspect ratio as the image size shown here, but both the height and width will be perfect squares. For example, an image shown here as 512x256 may only be 256x128 or even 128x64!

data.name: ViewMaxSpinner.ToolTip
data.value: How many times may this ad be viewed before it expires? Set to 0 for no limit.

data.name: MaxViewsCheckBox.ToolTip
data.value: Enable this checkbox to set an upper limit to the number of times this ad may be viewed before it expires.

data.name: ViewTimesSpinner.ToolTip
data.value: This is the number of times you have been recorded "viewing" this ad so far.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Minimum Time To Count As A View

data.name: VideoAdCheckbox.ToolTip
data.value:
Check this box if you intend to insert a BIK video ad. This only works on some games, like Trackmania Nations.
If this box is unchecked, then it will be assumed that you want a standard image (DDS) ad.
